{"tid":1716832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非新職業 - 執屋師","createTime":"2019-11-13T12:38:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T08:51:57.000Z","uid":75777,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d0ea2c8655fb5e2afb58376aa41bed13b011098e","tid":1716832,"uid":75777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:38:59.000Z","msg":"今日見到個街邊執垃圾既熱心黑衫呀叔<br />\n佢話佢好鍾意幫人收垃圾<br />\n如果馬路邊有雜物既話 不論大小<br />\n佢都會免費幫大家清走<br />\n<br />\n所以和理非今晚有個新任務:就係執屋<br />\n將你地屋企唔要唔用既雜物/垃圾放係馬路邊<br />\n幫幫黑衫呀叔滿足佢收垃圾既願望<br />\n記得唔好放d有個人資料既野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2143b532e8f135cd702081efe8e617971c0dbd","tid":1716832,"uid":75777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:45:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bc874f2f469bb669553e454594802bf870a645a","tid":1716832,"uid":322986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:45:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e54c3a2841c8fd09e104335241c53d1cccab526c","tid":1716832,"uid":19213,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:45:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想掉左屋企個櫃<br />\n買過新既"},{"pid":"d9da86dc231e2de8472a1bf3c5a5483e58555720","tid":1716832,"uid":8482,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:46:24.000Z","msg":"我有個夾萬唔用想抌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5189dee4c96abedd1171555863eef56ab304ab95","tid":1716832,"uid":284687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:37:04.000Z","msg":"樓下成日裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f86dbba9879613957798614854ae266af6685255","tid":1716832,"uid":75777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:42:01.000Z","msg":"集思廣益 有咩舊野好清?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽講「四電一腦」即日回收要徵費100蚊<br />\n唔係既可能要等3日<br />\n請自行判斷如何處理家中電子廢料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.是否能做到即日「拆舊換新」？<br />\n據環保署副署長吳文傑指出，現時沒有明文規定收集商最遲何時要上門收走舊電器。香港有 3 家持牌收集商，但大部分電器銷售商都委託了其中一間名為「歐綠保綜合環保有限公司」的收集商作除舊。由於歐綠保有 3 個工作天後提供除舊服務的服務承諾，所以當銷售商送新電器到家，<span style=\"color: red;\">歐綠保可能要在 3 日後才會過來回收舊電器</span>，未必做到同日「拆舊換新」。這代表，舊電器可能要在家裏放幾天才等到回收商。<br />\n亦因如此，有電器銷售商就乘機推出「升級服務」，只要每件貨多收 $100，就確保能夠做到同步即日拆舊換新。然而，這樣就會變成「雙重徵費」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5.能否自行丟棄舊電器？<br />\n在條例生效後，<span style=\"color: red;\">如市民將電器丟棄於垃圾站並不會構成刑責</span>。但環保署就不鼓勵市民自行棄置電器在垃圾站，因本年底堆填區亦會禁止接收「四電一腦」電器。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2113924/%E3%80%8C%E5%9B%9B%E9%9B%BB%E4%B8%80%E8%85%A6%E3%80%8D%E5%BE%AA%E7%92%B0%E5%86%8D%E9%80%A0%E5%BE%B5%E8%B2%BB%E6%87%B6%E4%BA%BA%E5%8C%85%EF%BC%81%E5%B0%8F%E5%BF%83%E8%A2%AB%E3%80%8C%E9%9B%99%E9%87%8D%E5%BE%B5%E8%B2%BB%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2113924%2F%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%259B%259B%25E9%259B%25BB%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%2585%25A6%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%25BE%25AA%25E7%2592%25B0%25E5%2586%258D%25E9%2580%25A0%25E5%25BE%25B5%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E6%2587%25B6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258C%2585%25EF%25BC%2581%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25BF%2583%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E3%2580%258C%25E9%259B%2599%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%25BE%25B5%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E3%2580%258D&d=eC9RRsiBNQJpYHZqEQI0QhjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=12771281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2113924/%E3%80%8C%E5%9B%9B%E9%9B%BB%E4%B8%80%E8%85%A6%E3%80%8D%E5%BE%AA%E7%92%B0%E5%86%8D%E9%80%A0%E5%BE%B5%E8%B2%BB%E6%87%B6%E4%BA%BA%E5%8C%85%EF%BC%81%E5%B0%8F%E5%BF%83%E8%A2%AB%E3%80%8C%E9%9B%99%E9%87%8D%E5%BE%B5%E8%B2%BB%E3%80%8D</a>"},{"pid":"d97360c373e1cdc986ae958c96dead25cefdf2fa","tid":1716832,"uid":263778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:45:05.000Z","msg":"一定會有和理非跟唔切燒法院<br />\n全部同我將文宣鋪天蓋地咁貼<br